svāhāṃ havirbhuji satīṃ giriśe tvadaṃśe ||1||
dakṣa: viriñca-tanaya: atha	Daksha, the son of Brahmaa, then
mano:-tanūjām labdhvā prasūtim-	getting Manu's daughter Prasooti, in marriage
